IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM sys.objects WHERE NAME = '[bulk1]' AND TYPE = 'U')
CREATE TABLE [dbo].[bulk1]
	(
	 vendorID nvarchar(30),
	 tpepPickupDateTime datetime2(7),
	 tpepDropoffDateTime datetime2(7),
	 passengerCount int,
	 tripDistance float,
	 puLocationId nvarchar(30),
	 doLocationId nvarchar(30),
	 startLon float,
	 startLat float,
	 endLon float,
	 endLat float,
	 rateCodeId int,
	 storeAndFwdFlag nvarchar(30),
	 paymentType nvarchar(30),
	 fareAmount float,
	 extra float,
	 mtaTax float,
	 improvementSurcharge nvarchar(30),
	 tipAmount float,
	 tollsAmount float,
	 totalAmount float
	)
WITH
	(
	DISTRIBUTION = ROUND_ROBIN,
	 CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
	 -- HEAP
	)
GO
